                                                            <li class="menu__item is-leaf leaf"><a href="/en/taxonomy/term/2543" title="From art to architecture, from film to fashion, British talent leads the world. Richard goes in search of the sources of British creativity, and meets Batman, Queen Elizabeth, and Puss in Boots along the way.

