" class="menu__link">Entrepreneurs are GREAT</a></li>
                                                            <li class="menu__item is-leaf leaf"><a href="/en/taxonomy/term/2546" title="Green issues are a global concern, but Britain is leading the way with great green innovation. This year&amp;#39;s Olympics will set a new record &amp;ndash;&amp;nbsp;as the most environmentally friendly games ever.

